SAFETY NOTICE FOR HVAC APPLICATIONS:

This software controls and monitors heating, ventilation, and air conditioning
(HVAC) equipment. While it implements safety features including fail-safes and
anti-condensation protection, it has NOT been formally certified for safety-critical
applications.

Users MUST:
1. Ensure proper installation by qualified personnel
2. Implement additional hardware safety measures (thermal fuses, etc.)
3. Regularly inspect for condensation and moisture damage
4. Comply with local electrical and building codes
5. Not rely solely on software for condensation prevention

The authors assume no liability for property damage, mold growth, or other
consequences of improper installation or operation.
